import {
    USER_LOADED,
    USER_LOADING,
    AUTH_ERR,
    LOGIN_SUCCESS,
    LOGIN_FAIL,
    LOGOUT_SUCCESS,

const initialState = {
    token: localStorage.getItem('token'),
    isAuthenticated: null,
    isLoading: false,
    user: null,
};
